column5: Hey Guys,  Heading up to fish one of my favs on the weekend in the Parry Sound area of GBay.  Judging by the Satellite picture it looks like they may finally have ice.  Can anyone confirm this?  PM if preferred.  Thanks in advance.  Tim
Most inland lake have ice. Can't say how good it is. You'd have to check it out as you go.
Any new info guys?  Heading up tomorrow.  Thanks Tim
